        <ul>
          <li>Free tuition fee for the entire study period</li>
          <li>Monthly stipend: HUF 43,700 for Bachelor's/Master's, HUF 140,000 for PhD</li>
          <li>Free dormitory accommodation or contribution to accommodation costs</li>
          <li>Medical insurance coverage</li>
        </ul>
